### REST Client extension is required: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client 
### baseUrl comes from "rest-client.environmentVariables"
### Environments are defined in .vscode/settings.json
### switch environment using shortcut Ctrl+Alt+E(Cmd+Alt+E for macOS), or press F1 and then select/type Rest Client: Switch Environment

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Interactive API docs (Scalar)
GET {{baseUrl}}/scalar/v1

###

### OpenAPI document
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json

###

### Run search - multiple locations
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": ["Manchester", "Bristol", "Edinburgh", "Cardiff", "Belfast"]
}

###

### Run search - single location
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": ["London"]
}

###

### Run search - includes not found location
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/searches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": ["London", "Nowhere", "Leeds"]
}

###

### Get supported locations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/locations
Accept: application/json

###

### List stored runs (newest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/searches
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a stored run by id
### 1) Run one of the POST /api/searches requests below
### 2) Copy response.runId into @runId
@runId = 947bfde6-008d-4a0b-9642-5ff3266cf372
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/searches/{{runId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Diff run vs explicit baseline
### Set both ids from previous POST responses or GET /api/searches output
@subjectRunId = 45cd0e9c-a7e2-4f62-a28d-42c0d2b4d5d1
@baselineRunId = 9a90d2a1-7e55-4f01-a2c1-c5d60f63a614
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/searches/{{subjectRunId}}/diff?against={{baselineRunId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Diff run vs most recent earlier run (omit against)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/searches/{{subjectRunId}}/diff
Accept: application/json



###
